snippet.title: Game & Watch - Bomb Sweeper (c)1987 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description:
This will be supported in MAME 0.212, thanks to algestam for the emulation and hydef for the artwork.

Artwork can be found at https://drive.google.com/open?id=1WLKcvynl0ky2mRL1UacA9yaiMTnNs4x5
